<s> <s> she didn’ t answer . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> angry , and half in love with her , and tremendously sorry , i turned away . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> one afternoon late in october i saw tom buchanan . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> he was walking ahead of me along fifth avenue in his alert , aggressive way , his hands out a little from his body as if to fight off interference , his head moving sharply here and there , adapting itself to his restless eyes . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> just as i slowed up to avoid overtaking him he stopped and began frowning into the windows of a jewellery store . </s> </s> 
<s> <s> suddenly he saw me and walked back , holding out his hand . </s> </s> 
